{"tid":1684840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"85%打工仔今年平均加薪3.6% 近半機構料明年加薪3%","createTime":"2019-10-31T09:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T09:49:07.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"970af592a5f2414e98c0ee1e1a6d4af3d1e647a1","tid":1684840,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:46:27.000Z","msg":"香港人力資源管理學會今公布2019年薪酬趨勢調查，結果顯示本港僱員今年平均加薪幅度為3.6%，較去年微升0.4百分點。<br />\n<br />\n該項調查訪問了94間來自15個不同行業的機構，涵蓋14.5萬名僱員，結果顯示受訪機構今年整體基本薪金平均加3.6%，較去年多0.4個百分點，扣除通脹後實質調升幅度為0.8%。獲加薪的僱員比例為84.9%，其餘僱員凍薪。<br />\n<br />\n調查指，當中近96%受訪機構在今年有加薪，3.3%的機構凍薪，1.1%機構減薪。中型公司(僱用500至1000名員工)平均調薪幅度最高達4%。<br />\n<br />\n受訪機構表示，僱主調整薪金時會考慮5大因素，依重要性排序為機構業績、個人工作表現、業務部門表現、市場薪酬調整狀況及香港經濟狀況。<br />\n<br />\n至於明年薪酬調整預測，近48%受訪機構表示暫時未有計劃，約51%機構預計明年僱員將獲加薪，預計平均加薪3.0%。約1%機構表示將會減薪。<br />\n<br />\n學會副會長孔于人指，雖然香港現時社會負面情緒不斷醞釀，但對明年上半年經濟影響不大，而且加薪與否仍需視乎機構業績、員工表現等因素，認為3%的升幅是一個穩健趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1125940/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-85-%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E4%BB%94%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA3-6-%E8%BF%91%E5%8D%8A%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E6%96%99%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1125940%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-85-%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BB%2594%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%259D%2587%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2596%25AA3-6-%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%258D%258A%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2596%25AA3&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=0e4754a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1125940%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-85-%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BB%2594%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%259D%2587%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2596%25AA3-6-%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%258D%258A%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2596%25AA3&h=9a044d22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1125940/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-85-%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E4%BB%94%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA3-6-%E8%BF%91%E5%8D%8A%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E6%96%99%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA3</a>"},{"pid":"0aeab5cfd21a2b8d910a45d60406f7dd72019166","tid":1684840,"uid":280493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/viH3p5U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FviH3p5U.gif&h=af690c61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4a32fd66e29fc0883b9fb75b53fd82419294a9b","tid":1684840,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/viH3p5U.gif\" />"}]}